1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Ever heard of the bends?

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:04,800
It’s more than just a diving term.

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:11,200
Decompression sickness happens when divers ascend too quickly, causing nitrogen bubbles to form in the bloodstream.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:14,800
Symptoms can range from joint pain to life-threatening conditions.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:18,800
But did you know it can also affect surface athletes?

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:24,400
Nitrogen comes from our air, and when you dive, it dissolves in your tissues.

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,800
Ascend slowly to avoid bubbles forming.

8
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,000
Awareness is key.

9
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,400
Know the risks and dive smart.

10
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:32,400
Your life depends on it!

11
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:34,800
Want to dive deeper into science?

12
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,800
Like and follow for more!
